{"tid":2340670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「暗黑郭雪芙」引退1年半閃電復出！　脫開浴衣甜喊2字激撩","createTime":"2020-12-25T16:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T20:00:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a74bfdb54bc8ba3d2013ffea986ab35ed6d5ab3c","tid":2340670,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"日本前AV女優水野朝陽有「暗黑郭雪芙」之稱，2018年12月初宣告引退。而她消失1年6個月，12月閃電復出，火速登上排行榜冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5357/d5357566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5357%2Fd5357566.jpg&h=cf591a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「暗黑郭雪芙」水野朝陽引退1年半閃電復出。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n水野朝陽現年30歲，擁有G罩杯爆乳身材，2年前引退後轉行從事美甲工作，也拍攝影片當YouTuber。她11月在YouTube發表重大消息，表示將復出專屬女優。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5357/d5357565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5357%2Fd5357565.jpg&h=41d61d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲水野朝陽在自己的YouTube透露自己要復出。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n緊接著水野朝陽在12月25日發行回歸後的第一支作品，且1月25日就會發表第二支影片。她同時在推特曬出片場花絮，拍攝浴衣短片，當腰帶緩緩落在榻榻米，鏡頭往上拍她逐漸脫開和服，裡面身穿粉色內衣，甜聲喊「復活」，令網友大噴鼻血，新作在網路排行火速衝上第一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5357/d5357567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5357%2Fd5357567.jpg&h=03f31ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲水野朝陽回歸拍AV，推特再曬辣照。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"5b686aea38079ef6bcd156a4b4e1dc88d467a4e6","tid":2340670,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"肥左咁多"},{"pid":"de52671c0fe1c150fb51147629835c815d3badbc","tid":2340670,"uid":92118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"生完仔再拍av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd5f1cd0e7a23cda737d4b1b5ba368a6298dda0","tid":2340670,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T17:26: